#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/webloop.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.webloop.PyodideFuture:1
msgid ""
"A :py:class:`~asyncio.Future` with extra :js:meth:`~Promise.then`, :js:meth:"
"`~Promise.catch`, and :js:meth:`finally_() <Promise.finally>` methods based "
"on the Javascript promise API. :py:meth:`~asyncio.loop.create_future` "
"returns these so in practice all futures encountered in Pyodide should be an "
"instance of :py:class:`~pyodide.webloop.PyodideFuture`."
msgstr ""

