#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/webloop.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.webloop.PyodideFuture.then:1
msgid ""
"When the Future is done, either execute onfulfilled with the result or "
"execute onrejected with the exception."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/webloop.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.webloop.PyodideFuture.then:4
msgid ""
"Returns a new Future which will be marked done when either the onfulfilled "
"or onrejected callback is completed. If the return value of the executed "
"callback is awaitable it will be awaited repeatedly until a nonawaitable "
"value is received. The returned Future will be resolved with that value. If "
"an error is raised, the returned Future will be rejected with the error."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/webloop.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.webloop.PyodideFuture.then:12
msgid ""
"A function called if the Future is fulfilled. This function receives one "
"argument, the fulfillment value."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/webloop.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.webloop.PyodideFuture.then:15
msgid ""
"A function called if the Future is rejected. This function receives one "
"argument, the rejection value."
msgstr ""

